This does NOT hide your IP, it only uses transparent proxies which can be seen, if you check on showmyip.com it will state your correct IP and also state you are connected through a proxy and show the proxy IP. This program does not use anonymous proxies, it will probably be ok for bypassing regioned websites like watching videos on sites outside their country but probably not worth it due to bandwith being eaten connecting to the proxy, If you plan to use this becuase you NEED to make sure your IP is not detected it is not the tool you are looking for.
